<div id="review_2664691505" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2664691505" />
    <a title="Cheryl James" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/14100063-cheryl-james"><img alt="Cheryl James" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1571941004p2/14100063.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2664691505?book_show_action=true">Jan 31, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Cheryl James" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Cheryl James" href="/user/show/14100063-cheryl-james">Cheryl James</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Audiobook " href="/book/show/10480613-devil-in-a-blue-dress">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2664691505" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16334150783806897193">I have been wanting to read this series for quite some time. I love the characters and their dialect. I am sure this is exactly how crime and criminals were protrayed back in the day. Even though things went bad in the end I love how the men spoke and hung out with each other. Money, women and power made them do crazy things. I look foward to reading the next 13 books!!</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

